Cabildo Insular de La Palma full extraordinary session of 12/30/1999

SUBJECT No. 4.- Approval of the logo of the Insular Council

Unanimously by the Councilors, the inclusion of the matter on the Agenda is ratified. Next, the Plenary, unanimously by the attendees, approves the Logo of this Hon. Insular Council, according to the graphic image that is included in the file, the technical characteristics of the logo being the following:

CHROMATISM: GREEN (PALM TREE), PANTONE COATED 369 (YELLOW 73.9 - PRO. BLUE 24.6 - BLACK 1.5) BLUE (OCEAN / CONTOUR), PANTONE COATED 2935. (PRO. BLUE 62.5 - REF. BLUE 37.5).
